Title: Relates to ovarian cancer research
Summary: Relates to ovarian cancer research; includes funding for ovarian cancer research and education programs.
LawCode: Amd §§2410, 2411, 2412 & 2413, Pub Health L; amd §97-yy, St Fin L; amd §§209-D & 627, Tax L; amd §404-q, V & T L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, the state finance law, the tax law and the vehicle and traffic law, in relation to ovarian cancer research
